WEBVTT

00:07:58.361 --> 00:08:01.162
and took over a class
at White Bear Lake Elementary School.

00:08:01.186 --> 00:08:03.973
Ananth Pai replaced
the standard curriculum

00:08:03.997 --> 00:08:06.871
with a video game based curriculum
of his own design,

00:08:06.895 --> 00:08:09.209
separating the kids into leaning styles

00:08:09.233 --> 00:08:12.178
and giving them Nintendo DS's
and computer games --

00:08:12.202 --> 00:08:14.428
everything off the shelf,
nothing custom --

00:08:14.452 --> 00:08:16.979
giving them Nintendo DS's
and computer games

00:08:17.003 --> 00:08:19.147
that were both individual
and social to play,

00:08:19.171 --> 00:08:21.418
that taught them math and language.

00:08:21.442 --> 00:08:23.257
Let me tell you what happened.

00:08:23.281 --> 00:08:27.020
In the space of 18 weeks,

00:08:27.044 --> 00:08:30.816
Mr. Pai's class went
from a below-3rd-grade level